{"word":"H6994 - קָטֹן - qâṭôn - kaw-tone' - Be a small","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָטֹן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>qâṭôn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-tone'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be a small"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பாத்திரன் அல்ல, குறை, கொஞ்சகாரியமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be small, to be insignificant"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be insignificant"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil) to make small, to reduce significantly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (rather denominative from <a href=\"#/H6996 - קָטָן - qâṭân - kaw-tawn'/6996\">H6996</a>); to <i>diminish</i>, that is, <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>diminutive</i> or (figuratively) <i>of no account: - </i>be a (make) small (thing), be not worthy."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6994 - קָטֹן - qâṭôn - kaw-tone'/6994\">H6994</a>, <a href=\"#/H6995 - קֹטֶן - qôṭen - ko'-ten/6995\">H6995</a>, <a href=\"#/H6996 - קָטָן - qâṭân - kaw-tawn'/6996\">H6996</a>, <a href=\"#/H6997 - קָטָן - Qâṭân - kaw-tawn'/6997\">H6997</a>"}]}